data.description: Wonderfully maintained home in Raeford! Gorgeous landscaping and a large front porch greets you while viewing this inviting home. Spacious foyer has hardwood floors and opens up to an expansive living room w/ fireplace and tons of natural light. Spacious kitchen with stainless steel appliances and great cabinet storage and counter space makes this perfect for entertaining. Large master bedroom w/ great closet space and en-suite bath has double vanities, jetted tub, and stand alone shower. Both guest bedrooms downstairs are generous in size and are accompanied by a nice guest bath with tub/shower combo and tile flooring. AMAZING space upstairs with new paint, which has a separate flex space w/closet that could be perfect for another bedroom, large bonus room, and full bath with new shower! Nice sized fenced backyard with large deck is the perfect place to spend time with the family, entertain, or watch those gorgeous Carolina sunsets! Welcome home.
